<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0785003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785003">（佛說）＋最【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0785004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785004">〔大〕－【宋】【明】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0785005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785005">〔唐〕－【聖】</note>
<note n="0785006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785006">詔＝制【聖】</note>
<note n="0785007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785007">誓＝逝【明】</note>
<note n="0785008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785008">覺＝見【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0785009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785009">贍＝瞻【宋】</note>
<note n="0785010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785010">縱廣＝從廣【聖】下同</note>
<note n="0785011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785011">箱＝廂【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0785012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0785012">側塞＝畟塞【元】【明】下同</note>
<note n="0786001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0786001">末香＝粖香【宋】【元】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0786002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0786002">薰＝熏【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0786003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0786003">逮＝建【聖】</note>
<note n="0786004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0786004">圍＝園【聖】</note>
<note n="0786005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0786005">後＋（如法梵身收其遺骨）【聖】</note>
<note n="0787001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787001">贍＝瞻【宋】【元】</note>
<note n="0787002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787002">天＝大【聖】</note>
<note n="0787003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787003">樂化＝化樂【三】【宮】，樂＋（變）【聖】</note>
<note n="0787004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787004">可＝不【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0787005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787005">若＋（有）【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0787006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787006">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0787007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0787007">妙＋（速證無上正等菩提）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0788001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0788001">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
<note n="0788002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0788002">（佛說）＋最【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0788003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0788003">經＋（一卷）【聖】</note>
</p>
